BOLO ADVENTURES I   v3.0   Requires EGA/VGA
Bolo Adventures is a mind boggling strategy 
game where the objective is to get Mr. Bolo 
out of 20 rooms of puzzles. Each room is 
filled with obstacles such as monsters, 
lasers, electric grills and more.  Unlike 
arcade games, Bolo Adventures isn't a contest 
of how fast you can acquire carpal tunnel 
syndrome by hammering on your keyboard, it's 
a test of your resourcefulness.
